Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,順滑感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,宣傳部的西岡先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,手機的畫面也可以快速滑動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:21:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是一種順滑感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不對
